.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6UcoZHBlQ80&d=rlXUku49MyaB5TbjwnmeDJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=78ba81cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:32:34.000Z","msg":"如果主人試過幫兔子洗澡，可能見過兔兔用後腳站起來，左右手上下方向擦。這時候兔子其實不是同你玩水，這個姿態是代表不高興，想主人不要理會牠。以下視頻可看到主人給兔子洗澡時，兔子在3:26被嚇暈：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6zkyjfOq36g&d=rlXUku49MyaB5TbjwnmeDJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=75e8e897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g</a>"},{"pid":"644cd2c3856fa2d91f7a9b700a983ac910f65c0d","tid":789583,"uid":37413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 惡晒兇終伏墓園 )<br />\n點解咁多垃圾上連登"},{"pid":"86af401d30364505c5f9c05b31a0fb4f7edaf2a9","tid":789583,"uid":56104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T06:14:27.000Z","msg":"我屋企隻兔兔養左一年多啲﹐由BB仔開始養。<br />\n<br />\n但我發覺佢由6個月大之後就唔俾我抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想請教下係點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}